well, ladies and gentlemen... i now have the funniest thing for all of you to hear. Today was one of my friends birthdays and a kinda of "tradition" i guess you could say, is to kidnapp the birthday person and take them out to eat or somethin like that. Today me and 3 other friends of mine went to this guys house to surprise him. We had an entire set up ready. There was cation tape (like the kind you find at a crime scene or something) surrounding his house and we set up cones around the "evidance". then we were gonna have a person lying on the floor like they were dead and we had 2 other people on standby and one person watching out for him. The two people on standby were supposed to put a bag over his head when he walked in. We were trying to work everything out for a while and then when we finally got it right we settled down and started talking. We had people switching off to see if he was coming. (keep in mind that we got to his house at 5p.m)then it turned to 8 and we started getting hungry so one of my friends and me went to get food and when we got back, he still hadn't come back. So then we were eating at his house with out him. which was really funny alone. Then someone said, "we should sing happy birthday" so we sang it. Then we finished eatinng and we just cleaned everything up and then left. lol!!! so weird but funny at the same time... well, miss you guys much and ttyl's
